netized, with relative\nmagnetization, $R_{\\rm B}\\approx1$, compared to the FS. These direct,\nmulti-frequency measurements of a refreshed RS spanning the optical to radio\nbands highlight the impact of radio and millimeter data in probing the\nproduction and nature of GRB jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2018 18:12:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-30"}
