 situations. Moreover, the convergence of the full\nmultigrid is also discussed with the constant kernel. The numerical experiments\nare performed to verify the convergence with only $\\mathcal{O}(N \\mbox{log} N)$\ncomplexity by the fast Fourier transform, where $N$ is the number of the grid\npoints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 01:04:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
