ing change has been understood\nin terms of Q-values of the transitions in the neutral and bare atoms.\nVerification of this branching change / flip phenomenon in bare atom decay\nmight be of interest for future experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 10:31:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Nov 2019 09:27:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-25"}
