des by a factor of two in about two days. Such a source will be\ndetectable by Satellite-ETCC if it occurs at a distance $\\leq 12$ Mpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 13:56:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Jan 2019 14:56:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-07"}
